headline: How the Coach Parent’s Stock Rally Squares With Its Soaring Earnings Multiple in 2025
summary: If you have been watching Tapestry’s stock, you are definitely not alone. Lately, the company has seen some impressive movement, up 10.3% in the last month and an astounding 156.2% over the past year. For anyone still deciding whether to buy, hold or sell, these kinds of returns are hard to ignore. In fact, over the last five years, Tapestry has delivered a whopping 575.3% return, easily catching the eye of seasoned investors and curious newcomers alike. So, what is driving all this momentum?...

headline: 3 S&P 500 Stocks We Approach with Caution
summary: The S&P 500 (^GSPC) is home to the biggest and most well-known companies in the market, making it a go-to index for investors seeking stability. But not all large-cap stocks are created equal - some are struggling with slowing growth, declining margins, or increased competition.
